As International Women's Day approaches, we are celebrating the women who are behind YouLi. 🎉

Jenny is located in Melbourne, Australia and joined our team in 2024 as a Business Analyst and Support Specialist. 

You might see her responding to support requests, but she is also involved in product testing, document writing, and onboarding our Australian customers. She has two adorable cats, and if you've ever been in a meeting with her, you might have seen them (they are not camera shy!) 🐱🐱
